Comprehend: Natural Language Processing.

ğŸ”¹ Azure
Azure ML: End-to-end ML development.
Cognitive Services: APIs for vision, speech, language.
Bot Services: Build intelligent bots.

ğŸ”· 7. DevOps & Developer Tools
